attributes.action: Illegal immigrants entering this country to have DNA taken
attributes.additional_details:
Often no one knows who these people are, so I think at the very least their DNA should be taken.
 
People who are arrested in this country have their DNA taken.
attributes.background: We think it should be mandatory for illegal immigrants entering this country to have their DNA taken.
